						<summary>

						<p>Broken slab set up near the field of Baḍatibayala-seṭṭi on the road to Chauḷikēri.</p>						

						<p>Circa 15th Century.</p>						

						<p>This damaged record seems to refer to an agreement. It refers to the Hattukēri of Bārakūru and to Nārāyaṇadēva.</p>						

						</summary>
