<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> <note n="516-2">The inscription is</note>
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Aṁ nyāyadalū hēḷida <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> bāḷidavanā <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> maryyādeya Ūrakēriyoḷage <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> gaḷanu kērikaṭaḷeyale Aḍūdu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> kōṭeyavaru <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> naḍisūdu Eṁdu kēryahalara dēvasva brahmasva hāne 20 <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> baṁbhattu kēryyahālarige hēḷidare <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> hattu kēriya halaru
<lb n="8"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> baha Arasu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> dirugoṁbudu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ḷidare Aramaneya ho <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> hattu kēryahalarige hēḷi Aḍakavanikki sōdeṁdu taṁmūḷage tāvu voḍaṁbaṭṭu bara
<lb n="11"/>du naṭṭa śilāśāṣana bārakūra hattukēryya halaravoppa śrīnārāyaṇa dēva <unclear>vopa</unclear>
<lb n="12"/>Āditya caṁdrā Anilō naḷaśca dyaurbhbhūmirāpōhradayaṁ yamaśca Ahacca rātriśca Ubhē
<lb n="13"/>ca saṁdhyē dharmmaśca jānāti narasyavrittaṁ śāsanake maṁgaḷamahā śrī śrī śrī śrī
<lb n="14"/>śrī
</p>

